            <li>Paired with <a>Richard Truab</a> on Thurs, Apr 11, 2013 on <a>backbone</a></li>
            <li>Paired with <a>Rose Millard</a> on Wed, Apr 10, 2013 on <a>backbone-relational</a></li>
          </ul>

          <h4 class="prepend-2">Starred Repos</h4>
